sequenceDiagram
  participant Q as query priority 20
  participant B as bind priority 20
  participant S as agc_shell priority 20
  participant Sch as rt_schedule

  loop no business but threads stay READY
    Q->>Q: check proc bitmap
    Q->>Sch: rt_thread_yield
    Sch-->>B: next same-priority ready thread
    B->>B: scan stop list / idle HCQD / task list
    B->>Sch: rt_thread_yield
    Sch-->>Q: next same-priority ready thread
  end

  Note over S: UART input wakes shell, but shell is inserted into same priority ready queue, not boosted above query/bind.
